value.raw: ; Define two 5-note scales with different pitches and partial overlap
; Use the 5-JI scale for p2 setting the base pitch to the pitch of d
; in its existing, scale, which is default.
; Exercise scale degree logic more thoroughly by having notes that
; extend outside the cycle (beyond b#). This ensures notes are sorted
; properly. These go up by fifths.
